questionsAndAnswers.question: What do I need to provide before we start the project?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Youâll need to provide your websiteâs domain and hosting details, any existing content (like text, images, or product details), and a brief description of your design preferences or any specific features you want to include.

questionsAndAnswers.question: Can you redesign my existing WordPress website?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Yes, I specialize in both designing new websites and redesigning existing ones. I can give your current site a fresh, modern look while improving its functionality and performance.

questionsAndAnswers.question: Do you use premium themes and plugins?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Yes, I use premium themes and plugins, including Elementor Pro and WooCommerce, to ensure your website has advanced features and a professional finish.

questionsAndAnswers.question: Will my website be mobile-friendly?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Absolutely! I create fully responsive websites that work seamlessly on all devices, including desktops, tablets, and smartphones, ensuring a great user experience for all visitors.

questionsAndAnswers.question: How long will it take to complete my website?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: The timeline depends on the complexity of the project. A basic e-commerce store typically takes 7-10 days, while more complex projects may take longer. Iâll provide a detailed timeline once I understand your requirements.

questionsAndAnswers.question: Will my website be SEO-friendly?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Yes, I will implement on-page SEO best practices to help your website rank better on search engines. This includes optimizing meta tags, images, and content structure.

questionsAndAnswers.question: Can you integrate payment gateways like PayPal or Stripe?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Yes, I can integrate multiple payment gateways, including PayPal, Stripe, and others, to ensure your customers can make secure and easy payments on your site.

questionsAndAnswers.question: What if I need help after the project is completed?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: I offer 24/7 support for any issues or questions that may arise after your website is live. Additionally, I provide ongoing maintenance services if you need regular updates or changes.
